node.text: regardez-moi petit requin avec les yeux qui brillent
Places I’ve been and those I’ve yet to discover

Version 2
I’m still going to do another variation 😆

I often think about lovers in winter. 
Chilly skin touching chilly skin. Icy cheeks brushing. Warm hearts beating.
A greeting. Layers of clothes, and of feelings. 
A thin divide 
I don’t know what happens next; my mind never gets that far
